data.description: Indulge in outdoor living at its finest! The Rapids is just minutes to the Savannah River! This splendid 5 Bedroom, 3 Bathroom home boasts an exceptional outdoor dining and entertaining space, making every day feel like vacation. With 4 bedrooms conveniently located on the main floor, including the primary suite, you'll enjoy easy living on one level! Upstairs, a fifth bedroom with a full bath offers versatility - it can be a guest suite, home office, or a private space for a family member. The heart of this home is its open floor plan, creating a seamless flow from the living room to the kitchen and dining area, allowing everyone to be part of the action! Step outside onto your back covered deck and you have an inviting area to entertain your guests! Whether you're enjoying a BBQ with friends, or simply having a family pool day, this space offers the perfect backdrop for making memories! Beyond the deck, you have a beautiful, in-ground gunite pool with Spa and 7 1/2 Ft infinity edge, providing a refreshing oasis for hot summer days! You will have tons of storage room in the huge walk-in attic! The Rapids offers great amenities including neighborhood pool, pickle ball courts, tennis courts, clubhouse and access to the Greenway! Conveniently located to Fort Gordon, SRS, Aiken and Augusta! Your home is where cherished memories are made. Don't miss the chance to make this one yours!
